        {
          "field_id": "the_american_joint_committee_on_cancer_ajcc_eighth_edition1_and_the_world_health_organization_who2_r",
          "label": "The American Joint Committee on Cancer (AJCC) eighth edition1 and the World Health Organization (WHO)2 recommend staging malignant phyllodes tumors according to guidelines established for soft tissue sarcomas – extremity and trunk. T category, N category and stage group assignments do not apply to benign or borderline phyllodes tumors and should only be reported if the tumor is malignant.",
